item.title: i lay my life down at your feet
item.description: I lay my life down at your feet You’re the only one I need, I turn to you and you are always there. In troubled times it’s you I seek, I put you first, that’s all I need, I humble all I am, all to you. One Way, Jesus! You’re the only one that I could live for (2) You are always, always there, Every how and everywhere, Your grace abounds so deeply within me.
